Since we do not have a limit on how long this crisis might continue. I want to write
a little program that helps companies update their prices on the spot as well as 
just a general way to ease things for the Lebanese population. 

Phases of the Project:

Objective:

1. Cause of the current inflation we need to develop a quick system that helps ease
computation problems.

2. Develop a system that works on multiple computers.

3. Adapt quickly to current market rate.

4. Deal with things holistically (calculate water,gas,electricity and basic amneties)